default:
Visibility - Accessible only within the same package.
Inheritance - no.
Example - 'class MyClass'.

public:
Visibility - Accessible within every package in the project.
Inheritance - Yes.
Example - 'public class MyClass'.

private:
public:
Visibility - Accessible only within the class.
Inheritance - no.
Example - 'private class MyClass'.

protected:
Visibility - Accessible within the same package and subclasses.
Inheritance - yes.
Example - 'private class MyClass'.